query:
UPDATE races SET
                    room = $1,
                    async_room1 = $2,
                    async_room2 = $3,
                    async_room3 = $4,
                    video_url = $5,
                    restreamer = $6,
                    video_url_fr = $7,
                    restreamer_fr = $8,
                    video_url_de = $9,
                    restreamer_de = $10,
                    video_url_pt = $11,
                    restreamer_pt = $12,
                    last_edited_by = $13,
                    last_edited_at = NOW()
                WHERE id = $14
